description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=1/3. Harass fish until they explode. Play through five unique mini games. Purchase over 30 different fish and make them explode. Unlock fish, music and other fishy things. More than 50 items to purchase in the fish store.
